Revision history for HomePilot

4.2.9 2016-06-13
    - wa-mmc-timeout: fix startup
    - hp-blob
        * SceneHandler: Remove queue entry when provider throw an exception

4.2.8 2016-06-09
    - hp2sm
        * networkmgr: fix leading and trailing spaces in ssid's
        * networkmgr: fix backslashes and quotes in ssid's
        * networkmgr: add wpa2-psk routes using body parameters
        * networkmgr: don't disable active network interfaces
    - hp-blob
        * networkmanager: fixed special character issue for wlan config
        * adjusted favorite tiles to device tiles
        * ZWaveProvider: Remove configuration of wakeup time for FTK
        * Web-UI: Adjustment of wlan input formular
        * ZWaveProvider: Solve problem with setting of wakeup interval
        * DF-Provider: Support of PushButton command
        * adapted favorite device/scene placement to two columns
        * removed favorite container size calculation
        * Web-UI: Change the commands when slider bottons are pressed for blade function
        * Web-UI: New concept for config text input field when input not valid
    - zway: disabled vdev support
    - busybox/ifplugd: fix wlan boot up issue
    - nginx: cleanup nginx configuration
    - nginx: configure proxy timeouts for the root location (fix backup issue)
    - nginx: disable http_stub_status_module
    - prd-flash: improve regex to merge wpa_supplicant.conf
    - add workaround for mmc0 timeouts

4.2.7 2016-06-01
    - errhlp: disable the error led
    - hp2sm
        * networkmgr: apply nodename to all network interfaces
    - hp-blob
        * Web-UI: Fix special characters in wifi ssid, pw not working
        * Web-UI: Adjusted width of favorite device tiles
        * Web-UI: Allow only inputs in the range of 4 to 40 degrees for sensor config
        * DF-Provider: Insert waiting function after DF command was sent
        * Web-UI: Repair automatic button handling
        * CameraDeviceProvider: Get the correct uid from homepilot for camera pictures
        * DF-Devices: Definition of wind, rain and sun program in status capabilities
        * Status handler: Definition of wind, rain and sun program in status capabilities
    - duofern-service
        * Sun-program for dimmer: Change bit position for sun program state

